T02TD1964E:101a-0: @101a ` // gshin rje gshed nag po'i 'khor lo'i man ngag bzhugs//
T02TD1964E:101a-2: # // 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1964E:101a-3: las gang byed kyang dang po bsnyen pa la 'jug par bya ste /
T02TD1964E:101a-5: rang nyid rim pa bzhin du h'um la gshin rje'i rgyal po gzugs khro bo 'jigs byed chen po zhal gsum pa /
T02TD1964E:101a-10: g-yas zla ba lta bu dkar po /
T02TD1964E:101a-11: g-yon padma dmar po lta bu'o //
T02TD1964E:101a-12: phyag g-yas dang po na rdo rje /
T02TD1964E:101a-14: gsum pa ni gri gug 'dzin pa'o //
T02TD1964E:101a-15: phyag g-yon gyi dang po na 'khor lo /
T02TD1964E:101a-18: thod pa rlon pa'i do shal dang /
T02TD1964E:101a-19: thod dang thod dum gyi gdu bu dang /
T02TD1964E:101a-25: ma he'i steng na nyi ma'i gdan la g-yas bskum /
T02TD1964E:101a-27: gsus pa thur du bshal ba /
T02TD1964E:101a-28: zhal gdangs shing ljags 'dril ba ste /
T02TD1964E:101b-0: 'jigs pa'i tshogs kun @101b 'jigs par byed pa /
T02TD1964E:101b-1: skra kham ser me dpung 'bar ba lta bu gyen du 'khyil ba sma ra dang smin ma ser po dang ldan zhing mche ba gtsigs pa /
T02TD1964E:101b-2: spyan dmar po shin tu 'jigs par bzlog pa kha spu'i bu ga thams cad nas mi bskyod pa'i gzugs dpag tu med pa rgyun du 'phro ba /
T02TD1964E:101b-3: 'od dang 'od zer dus mtha'i bskal ba'i me ltar 'bar ba dang ldan pa bsgoms la /
T02TD1964E:101b-4: de nas aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1964E:101b-6: lha la ma yengs pa tsam gyis zlos kyang rung ste /
T02TD1964E:101b-8: mtshan ma bzang po yang yang mthong ba'i bar du bzlas so //
T02TD1964E:101b-10: las kun la de ltar bye brag med par dang por mthun par bya'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-11: de ltar las su byed pa'i dus su bye brag tu bya ste /
T02TD1964E:101b-12: 'di ltar zhi bar byed na rang lha'i gzugs su bsgyur te /
T02TD1964E:101b-13: mdog dkar por bsgyur ba dang /
T02TD1964E:101b-14: byams pa'i sems dang ldan par byas la /
T02TD1964E:101b-15: bdud rtsi'i rgyud las 'byung ba ltar snga dro'i dus su /
T02TD1964E:101b-16: shing lo'am gro ga'i shun pa gsal //
T02TD1964E:101b-17: skyes pa zhi bar byed pa gur kum gyis bri /
T02TD1964E:101b-18: bud med zhi bar byed pa'i gi wang gis bri ba ni /
T02TD1964E:101b-19: 'khor lo rim pa bzhi bris la /
T02TD1964E:101b-20: dbus la re mig dgu dgur bya ste //
T02TD1964E:101b-21: de yi phyi rim bcu gnyis mig / de yi phyi rim bcu drug mig / tha ma thod pas bskor ba bri //
T02TD1964E:101b-22: dbus kyi re'u mig dgur dgod pa //
T02TD1964E:101b-23: dbus char ya dang shar char kshe //
T02TD1964E:101b-24: lho yi mig la ma bri'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-25: nub mig mi bri shar du'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-26: de dag g-yas skor dag tu 'dod //
T02TD1964E:101b-27: de mtshams re'u mig bzhi po la //
T02TD1964E:101b-28: sa bon gnyis par mig bcug la //
T02TD1964E:101b-29: g-yon skor du ni bri bar bya //
T02TD1964E:101b-30: zhi ba'i sa bon aom sv'a h'a //
T02TD1964E:101b-31: rgyas pa'i sa bon boo shat /
T02TD1964E:101b-32: rmongs pa'i sa bon lam yin no //
T02TD1964E:101b-33: dbang gi ho ste mngon spyod h'um /
T02TD1964E:101b-34: pho dgug dza: la mo dgug hr'i: //
T02TD1964E:101b-35: de ltar bye brag shes byas la //
T02TD1964E:101b-36: ma nor bar ni legs par bri /
T02TD1964E:101b-37: de yi phyi mar 'khor lo ni //
T02TD1964E:101b-38: re'u mig bcu gnyis pa de la //
T02TD1964E:101b-39: yi ge g-yon skor du bkod pa //
T02TD1964E:101b-40: shar gyi re'u mi gnas bzung ba'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-43: na yo ni ra rnams so //
T02TD1964E:101b-44: de yi phyi rim 'khor lo ni //
T02TD1964E:101b-45: re'u mig bcu drug pa de la //
T02TD1964E:101b-46: shar gyi re'u mig nas brtsams nas //
T02TD1964E:101b-47: g-yas skor du ni bri bar bya //
T02TD1964E:101b-49: @102/3a * // sngags dang ming dang bskul tshig dang //
T02TD1964E:101b-50: ldan par shar gyi re'u mig la'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-51: de yi 'og ma'i re'u mig la //
T02TD1964E:101b-52: sa bon gnyis dang ming bcug bri //
T02TD1964E:101b-53: de bzhin re'u mig bcu drug la //
T02TD1964E:101b-54: spel zhing spel zhing bra bar bya'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-55: de ltar bris pa'i 'khor lo de //
T02TD1964E:101b-56: lugs dang lugs min gnyis su bya //
T02TD1964E:101b-57: chu zhing mnyam po gnyis su bya'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-58: khyad par du ni 'og ma la //
T02TD1964E:101b-59: sngags kyi mtha' ru phat gzhag go //
T02TD1964E:101b-60: de bzhin kha sbyar bya lugs ni //
T02TD1964E:101b-61: steng 'og so so'i yig sngags dag / mthun mthun so sor mgo sprad sbyar //
T02TD1964E:101b-62: de ni zlum por dril bya la //
T02TD1964E:101b-63: drag min dag la spra tshil gyis ;
T02TD1964E:101b-64: / phyi rol g-yogs pa rab byas la //
T02TD1964E:101b-65: de nas kham phor mnyam po gnyis //
T02TD1964E:101b-66: byas pas gcig tu rtsi mar dang //
T02TD1964E:101b-67: sbrang rtsi bsres pas bkang ba yi //
T02TD1964E:101b-68: nang du kha sbyar 'khor lo gzhug / de nas kham phor gcig gis ni //
T02TD1964E:101b-69: steng nas kha ni dgab par bya'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-70: de la las kyi mdog mthun pa'i //
T02TD1964E:101b-71: skud pa'i khris ni mdun du dkri //
T02TD1964E:101b-72: de nas rang lha'i las mthun pa'i //
T02TD1964E:101b-73: gzugs su rang nyid rab byas te //
T02TD1964E:101b-74: 'khor lo kha sbyar steng du yang //
T02TD1964E:101b-75: de 'dra'i gshin rje ru bsams la //
T02TD1964E:101b-76: de la me tog dri chab mdog dang mthun pa yi //
T02TD1964E:101b-77: bdug spos la sogs mchod byas la //
T02TD1964E:101b-78: bsgrung bya zla ba la bzhag ste //
T02TD1964E:101b-79: rang nyid zla ba'i rdo rje yis //
T02TD1964E:101b-80: lte ba'i h'um las rang 'dra ba'i //
T02TD1964E:101b-81: khro bo du ma ye shes kyi //
T02TD1964E:101b-82: chus gang bum pa las mthun mdog /'dzin pa spros pa slar bsdus te //
T02TD1964E:101b-83: bsgrub bya'i spyi bor dbang bskur bas //
T02TD1964E:101b-85: thun mtshams bzhi la gsang sngags ni //
T02TD1964E:101b-86: ming dang bskul tshig bcas pa bzlog / dbang la bye brag tu bya ba //
T02TD1964E:101b-87: tsandan dmar dang srin lag khrag / rgya skyegs khu ba btsag kyang rung //
T02TD1964E:101b-88: dmar po'i rdzas kyis bri bar bya //
T02TD1964E:101b-89: bud med dgug la khyad par ni //
T02TD1964E:101b-90: dur khrod kyi ni ras ma la //
T02TD1964E:101b-92: bud med bhandha kha sbyar gzhug / rmongs la khyad par dur ras la //
T02TD1964E:101b-93: ldong ros kyis bris kham phor gzhug / de steng sum las ri rab dang //
T02TD1964E:101b-94: lam ser sna tshogs rdo rje yi //
T02TD1964E:101b-95: steng du lha bskyed kun la sbyar //
T02TD1964E:101b-96: rmongs rgyas ser po dbang dgug dmar //
T02TD1964E:101b-97: drag dang tshar gcad @102/3b gnag gzhi dkar //
T02TD1964E:101b-98: de ltar kha dog bye brag sbyar //
T02TD1964E:101b-99: drag po khyad par dbye ba ni //
T02TD1964E:101b-100: dur khrod ras la 'khor lo ni //
T02TD1964E:101b-101: gong dang mthun par bri bar bya //
T02TD1964E:101b-102: snag tsha ske tshe tsha dang dug / nim pa sga dang pi pi ling //
T02TD1964E:101b-103: na le sham yungs kar nag dmar //
T02TD1964E:101b-104: shing nag chan po'i sa bon dang //
T02TD1964E:101b-105: tsi tra ka yi khu ba dang //
T02TD1964E:101b-106: srin lag khrag dang dur khrod sol //
T02TD1964E:101b-107: de rnams rnyed tshad bsres pas bya //
T02TD1964E:101b-108: snyu gu bya rog sgro rtses bya //
T02TD1964E:101b-109: des ni 'khor lo legs bris la //
T02TD1964E:101b-110: kha sbyar dril te rgyu rnams la //
T02TD1964E:101b-111: byas pa'i gzugs brnyan snying gar gzhug / de nas gzhan yang ri rtse yi //
T02TD1964E:101b-112: sa ni shin tu skam po la //
T02TD1964E:101b-113: rigs ngan kha nas chu blangs sbru //
T02TD1964E:101b-114: sbrus pa'i 'dag pa de las ni //
T02TD1964E:101b-115: gshin rje'i rgyal po'i gzugs byas te //
T02TD1964E:101b-116: g-yas bskum g-yon brkyang bgrad pa la //
T02TD1964E:101b-117: g-yas pa tho ba zhags pa g-yon //
T02TD1964E:101b-118: gsus pa che la thur bshal ba //
T02TD1964E:101b-119: byas la mdun du gzhag par bya'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-120: mar ngo'i tshes brgyad bcu bzhi la //
T02TD1964E:101b-121: las dag nyin phyed nam phyed na'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-122: rang nyid khro gzugs khro sems kyis //
T02TD1964E:101b-123: lho ru kha bltas stan pa der 'dug / de nas rang snying h'um yig las //
T02TD1964E:101b-124: khro rgyal mdog nag zhal gcig pa //
T02TD1964E:101b-125: phyag gnyis 'khor lo lcags kyu thogs //
T02TD1964E:101b-126: mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin spros la //
T02TD1964E:101b-127: bsgrub bya'i go cha mtshon cha kun //
T02TD1964E:101b-128: phrogs te drangs nas rang snying gi / sa bon h'um la thim par bsam //
T02TD1964E:101b-129: tshul des de yi khyim stong bsam //
T02TD1964E:101b-130: de nas yang ni rang snying las //
T02TD1964E:101b-131: gong ltar khro bo rab spros pas //
T02TD1964E:101b-132: bsgrub bya drangs nas sngags pa yis //
T02TD1964E:101b-133: mdun du kha dog nag po ru //
T02TD1964E:101b-134: gzugs brnyan la bstim gsal po ru //
T02TD1964E:101b-135: de la sna tshogs nad rnams kyis //
T02TD1964E:101b-136: mnar bar bsam zhing gcer bu dang //
T02TD1964E:101b-137: rab tu 'dar zhing sems gdung dang //
T02TD1964E:101b-138: lus ni shin tu sdug bsngal zhing //
T02TD1964E:101b-139: lus la shu ba ral gri mda' //
T02TD1964E:101b-140: sta re la sogs mtshon rnams kyis //
T02TD1964E:101b-141: tshabs cher gzer bar bsam par bya'o //
T02TD1964E:101b-142: de yang rlung nag ches g-yengs pas //
T02TD1964E:101b-143: shin tu grang bas 'khyags par bsam //
T02TD1964E:101b-144: me chen rab 'bar bas bskor te //
T02TD1964E:101b-145: rab tshabs kyang gdung bar bsam //
T02TD1964E:101b-146: de la'ang khyi dang seng ge wa //
T02TD1964E:101b-147: stag dang bya rog bya rgod dang //
T02TD1964E:101b-148: mchu rings sogs pa rngam tshul du //
T02TD1964E:104a-2: de nas gzugs brnyan de la ni //
T02TD1964E:104a-3: tsher ma rnon po rab blangs la //
T02TD1964E:104a-4: bar mtshams med par rab phug la //
T02TD1964E:104a-5: tsha ba'i lde gus rab bskus la //
T02TD1964E:104a-6: de nas gshin rje'i lto bar gzhug / de gsus bsgrub bya rab bsams la //
T02TD1964E:104a-7: rang snying khro bo mtshon thogs spro //
T02TD1964E:104a-8: de yis gshin rje'i gzugs gnas pa'i //
T02TD1964E:104a-9: bsgrub bya de bsad de'i sha khrag / zos 'thungs rus chog rkang gzhibs bsam //
T02TD1964E:104a-10: sprul pa bya rgod gzugs can gyis //
T02TD1964E:104a-11: nang khrol phyung khyer khar song bsam //
T02TD1964E:104a-12: las ngan byed de dmyal bar 'gro //
T02TD1964E:104a-13: mi gdung bya phyir de yi sems //
T02TD1964E:104a-14: rgyal ba'i gzugs su rang snying gi /'od kyis bsdus te rgyal ba yi //
T02TD1964E:104a-15: zhing sar khyer nas bkod par bsam //
T02TD1964E:104a-16: de ltar las kyi tshul de nyid //
T02TD1964E:104a-17: sdig pa can la dgongs pas gsungs //
T02TD1964E:104a-18: yang na gshin rje'i sgom lugs gzhan //
T02TD1964E:104a-19: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g-yas zhags pa //
T02TD1964E:104a-20: g-yon pa sdigs mdzub ldan pa la //
T02TD1964E:104a-21: dbu rgyan rang rang rigs bdag go //
T02TD1964E:104a-22: so so'i sngags kyi dbye ba ni //
T02TD1964E:104a-23: gsal bar bris pa 'di yin no //
T02TD1964E:104a-24: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1964E:104a-25: che ge mo sh'anti dku ru sv'a h'a /
T02TD1964E:104a-26: 'di ni las kyi bzlas pa dang //
T02TD1964E:104a-27: 'khor lo rtsibs bcu drug pa spel la //
T02TD1964E:104a-29: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat boo shat che ge mo bushtim ku ru boo shat dang //
T02TD1964E:104a-30: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat /
T02TD1964E:104a-31: ho che ge mo dza: dza hr'i wa sham ku ru ho:/
T02TD1964E:104a-32: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat /
T02TD1964E:104a-33: boo shat che ge mo sha na ya ba sha na ya /
T02TD1964E:104a-34: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat /
T02TD1964E:104a-35: hr'i: bud med che ge mo a'a karsha ya hr'i:/
T02TD1964E:104a-36: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat dza:/
T02TD1964E:104a-37: skyes pa che go mo la a'a karsha ya dza:/
T02TD1964E:104a-38: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat /
T02TD1964E:104a-39: lam che ge mo rang gi gnas dang bcas pa //
T02TD1964E:104a-42: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'u m h'um phat phat h'um che ge mo m'a ra ya phat /
T02TD1964E:104a-45: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat /
T02TD1964E:104a-46: h'um che ge mo m'a ra ya h'um /
T02TD1964E:104a-48: boo shat che ge mo boo shat /
T02TD1964E:104a-51: dza: che ge mo dza: hr'i: che ge mo hr'i: dbus kyi re'u mig grva bzhi dang //
T02TD1964E:104a-52: gsum pa bcu drug pa la ni //
T02TD1964E:104b-0: spel ba'i sngags @104b su shes par bya //
T02TD1964E:104b-1: ring po dag ni spel ba ste //
T02TD1964E:104b-2: las dus bzlas pa de ltar ro //
T02TD1964E:104b-3: gru bzhi dang gsum pa'i phyogs bcu drug spel lo //
T02TD1964E:104b-4: gshed nag 'khor lo'i man ngag / slob dpon chen po n'a ga bo dhis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1964E:104b-6: // / lo ts'a ba dge slong chos rab kyis bsgyur /
